r":"anonymous","dateUpdated":"2026-06-06T08:55:14+0000","config":{"colWidth":12,"enabled":true,"results":{},"editorSetting":{"language":"python"},"editorMode":"ace/mode/python"},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"results":{"code":"SUCCESS","msg":[{"type":"TEXT","data":"+---+-----+\n|age|count|\n+---+-----+\n| 31|    2|\n| 32|    1|\n| 33|    3|\n| 36|    1|\n| 37|    1|\n| 38|    2|\n| 39|    4|\n| 40|    2|\n+---+-----+\n\n"}]},"apps":[],"jobName":"paragraph_1780736105127_169330098","id":"20260606-085505_1353084946","dateCreated":"2026-06-06T08:55:05+0000","dateStarted":"2026-06-06T08:55:14+0000","dateFinished":"2026-06-06T08:55:17+0000","status":"FINISHED","progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"$$hashKey":"object:20736"},{"text":"%spark2.sql\n\nSELECT age, count\nFROM scientists_age\n","user":"anonymous","dateUpdated":"2026-06-06T08:56:18+0000","config":{"colWidth":12,"enabled":true,"results":{"0":{"graph":{"mode":"stackedAreaChart","height":300,"optionOpen":true},"helium":{}}},"editorSetting":{"language":"sql"},"editorMode":"ace/mode/sql"},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"results":{"code":"SUCCESS","msg":[{"type":"TABLE","data":"age\tcount\n31\t2\n32\t1\n33\t3\n36\t1\n37\t1\n38\t2\n39\t4\n40\t2\n"}]},"apps":[],"jobName":"paragraph_1780736132413_1122615279","id":"20260606-085532_1371976017","dateCreated":"2026-06-06T08:55:32+0000","dateStarted":"2026-06-06T08:55:36+0000","dateFinished":"2026-06-06T08:55:44+0000","status":"FINISHED","progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"$$hashKey":"object:20737"},{"text":"%md\n### Interpretation\n\nThis result identifies a specific demographic subgroup: users who work as scientists and are between 30 and 40 years old.\n\nSuch filtered queries are useful when analyzing behavioural patterns for particular professions or age segments.\n\n","user":"anonymous","dateUpdated":"2026-06-06T08:01:05+0000","config":{"colWidth":12,"enabled":true,"results":{},"editorSetting":{"language":"markdown","editOnDblClick":true},"editorMode":"ace/mode/markdown","editorHide":true,"tableHide":false},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"results":{"code":"SUCCESS","msg":[{"type":"HTML","data":"<h3>Interpretation</h3>\n<p>This result identifies a specific demographic subgroup: users who work as scientists and are between 30 and 40 years old.</p>\n<p>Such filtered queries are useful when analyzing behavioural patterns for particular professions or age segments.</p>\n"}]},"apps":[],"jobName":"paragraph_1780732850329_1906194270","id":"20260606-080050_304343892","dateCreated":"2026-06-06T08:00:50+0000","dateStarted":"2026-06-06T08:01:05+0000","dateFinished":"2026-06-06T08:01:06+0000","status":"FINISHED","progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"$$hashKey":"object:20738"},{"text":"%md\r\n## Conclusion\r\n\r\nThis notebook demonstrates a complete big data pipeline using **Apache Spark**, **HDFS**, and **Cassandra** on the MovieLens 100K dataset.\r\n\r\nThe workflow covered:\r\n- loading raw data from HDFS,\r\n- creating RDDs,\r\n- transforming RDDs into DataFrames,\r\n- cleaning and preprocessing,\r\n- storing processed data in Cassandra,\r\n- validating the data by reading it back into Spark,\r\n- and performing analytical queries using Spark SQL.\r\n\r\nThe results provide insight into:\r\n- average movie ratings,\r\n- the highest-rated movies,\r\n- active users and their favourite genres,\r\n- users younger than 20,\r\n- and scientists aged 30 to 40.\r\n\r\nOverall, the pipeline shows how distributed storage and processing tools can be integrated to support scalable data analytics.\r\n","user":"anonymous","dateUpdated":"2026-06-06T08:04:00+0000","config":{"colWidth":12,"enabled":true,"results":{},"editorSetting":{"editOnDblClick":true,"language":"markdown"},"editorMode":"ace/mode/markdown","editorHide":true,"tableHide":false},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"results":{"code":"SUCCESS","msg":[{"type":"HTML","data":"<h2>Conclusion</h2>\n<p>This notebook demonstrates a complete big data pipeline using <strong>Apache Spark</strong>, <strong>HDFS</strong>, and <strong>Cassandra</strong> on the MovieLens 100K dataset.</p>\n<p>The workflow covered:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>loading raw data from HDFS,</li>\n<li>creating RDDs,</li>\n<li>transforming RDDs into DataFrames,</li>\n<li>cleaning and preprocessing,</li>\n<li>storing processed data in Cassandra,</li>\n<li>validating the data by reading it back into Spark,</li>\n<li>and performing analytical queries using Spark SQL.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The results provide insight into:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>average movie ratings,</li>\n<li>the highest-rated movies,</li>\n<li>active users and their favourite genres,</li>\n<li>users younger than 20,</li>\n<li>and scientists aged 30 to 40.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Overall, the pipeline shows how distributed storage and processing tools can be integrated to support scalable data analytics.</p>\n"}]},"apps":[],"jobName":"paragraph_1780732888052_507509425","id":"20260606-080128_478024277","dateCreated":"2026-06-06T08:01:28+0000","dateStarted":"2026-06-06T08:04:00+0000","dateFinished":"2026-06-06T08:04:00+0000","status":"FINISHED","progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"$$hashKey":"object:20739"},{"text":"","user":"anonymous","dateUpdated":"2026-06-06T08:44:07+0000","config":{"colWidth":12,"enabled":true,"results":{},"editorSetting":{"language":"scala"},"editorMode":"ace/mode/scala"},"settings":{"params":{},"forms":{}},"apps":[],"jobName":"paragraph_1780733039767_-1149052417","id":"20260606-080359_1146352866","dateCreated":"2026-06-06T08:03:59+0000","status":"READY","errorMessage":"","progressUpdateIntervalMs":500,"$$hashKey":"object:20740"}],"name":"Spark_Cassandra_Movielens_Data","id":"2MUW92MPB","angularObjects":{"2CHS8UYQQ:shared_process":[],"2C8A4SZ9T_livy2:shared_process":[],"2CK8A9MEG:shared_process":[],"2C4U48MY3_spark2:shared_process":[],"2CKAY1A8Y:shared_process":[],"2CKEKWY8Z:shared_process":[]},"config":{"isZeppelinNotebookCronEnable":false,"looknfeel":"simple","personalizedMode":"false"},"info":{}}